name: s_m_Load_Master_Agency_Detail_from_Import
description: Session to load the Master_Agency_Detail from mysql data to stage to SQLserver for EDW reports using SCD type 2

parameters.name: $Src_Agency_Group_Gw_Domain_AgencyEmail$
parameters.label: DBConnection_SRC
parameters.customQuery:
select
        Agency_Code                ,
        Agency_Name                ,
        Agency_Address             ,
        Agency_City                ,
        Agency_State               ,
        Agency_Zip                 ,
        Agency_Contact_Phone       ,
        Agency_Contact_Fax         ,
        Agency_fieldman            ,
        Agency_Group_Code          ,
        Field_Representative_Number,
        Field_Representative_State ,
        Field_Representative_Name  ,
        Agency_Email1              ,
        Agency_Email2              ,
        Agency_Email3              ,
        Agency_Email4              ,
        Agency_Email5              ,
        Agency_Email6              ,
        Agency_Email7              ,
        Agency_Email8              ,
        Agency_Email9              ,
        Agency_Email10             ,
        Status                     ,
        M_Address1                 ,
        M_Address2                 ,
        M_City                     ,
        M_State                    ,
        M_Zip
from
        (
                select distinct
                        LTRIM(RTRIM(ta.agency_nup ))                                                       Agency_Nup        ,
                        LTRIM(RTRIM(ta.agency_num ))                                                       Agency_Code       ,
                        LTRIM(RTRIM(ta.agency_name))                                                       Agency_Name       ,
                        LTRIM(RTRIM(CONCAT(COALESCE(ta.agency_str_1, ''), COALESCE(ta.agency_str_2, '')))) as Agency_Address ,
                        LTRIM(RTRIM(ta.agency_city))                                                       Agency_City       ,
                        LTRIM(RTRIM(ta.agency_st))                                                         Agency_State      ,
                        case
                        when
                                LTRIM(RTRIM(ta.agency_zip)) is null
                                or len(LTRIM(RTRIM(ta.agency_zip)))=0
                        then
                                null
                        else
                                LTRIM(RTRIM(ta.agency_zip))
                        end as Agency_Zip ,
                        case
                        when
                                replace(LTRIM(RTRIM(ta.agency_contact_phone)),' ','-') is null
                                or len(replace(LTRIM(RTRIM(ta.agency_contact_phone)),' ','-'))=0
                        then
                                null
                        else
                                replace(LTRIM(RTRIM(ta.agency_contact_phone)),' ','-')
                        end as Agency_Contact_Phone ,
                        case
                        when
                                replace(LTRIM(RTRIM(ta.agency_contact_fax)),' ','-') is null
                                or len(replace(LTRIM(RTRIM(ta.agency_contact_fax)),' ','-'))=0
                        then
                                null
                        else
                                replace(LTRIM(RTRIM(ta.agency_contact_fax)),' ','-')
                        end                             as Agency_Contact_Fax ,
                        LTRIM(RTRIM(tg.groups_number )) Agency_Group_Code     ,
                        CASE
                        WHEN
                                LTRIM(RTRIM(gw.fieldrep)) IS NULL
                                OR LEN(LTRIM(RTRIM(gw.fieldrep)))=0
                        THEN
                                NULL
                        ELSE
                                LTRIM(RTRIM(gw.fieldrep))
                        end as Field_Representative_Number ,
                        CASE
                        WHEN
                                LTRIM(RTRIM(gw.fieldrep_state)) IS NULL
                                OR LEN(LTRIM(RTRIM(gw.fieldrep_state)))=0
                        THEN
                                NULL
                        ELSE
                                LTRIM(RTRIM(gw.fieldrep_state))
                        end as Field_Representative_State ,
                        CASE
                        WHEN
                                LTRIM(RTRIM(dd.DOM_name)) IS NULL
                                OR LEN(LTRIM(RTRIM(dd.DOM_name)))=0
                        THEN
                                NULL
                        ELSE
                                LTRIM(RTRIM(dd.DOM_name))
                        end as Field_Representative_Name ,
                        CASE
                        WHEN
                                LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr1)) IS NULL
                                OR LEN(LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr1)))=0
                        THEN
                                NULL
                        ELSE
                                LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr1))
                        END as Agency_Email1 ,
                        CASE
                        WHEN
                                LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr2)) IS NULL
                                OR LEN(LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr2)))=0
                        THEN
                                NULL
                        ELSE
                                LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr2))
                        END as Agency_Email2 ,
                        CASE
                        WHEN
                                LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr3)) IS NULL
                                OR LEN(LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr3)))=0
                        THEN
                                NULL
                        ELSE
                                LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr3))
                        END as Agency_Email3 ,
                        CASE
                        WHEN
                                LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr4)) IS NULL
                                OR LEN(LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr4)))=0
                        THEN
                                NULL
                        ELSE
                                LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr4))
                        END as Agency_Email4 ,
                        CASE
                        WHEN
                                LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr5)) IS NULL
                                OR LEN(LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr5)))=0
                        THEN
                                NULL
                        ELSE
                                LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr5))
                        END as Agency_Email5 ,
                        CASE
                        WHEN
                                LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr6)) IS NULL
                                OR LEN(LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr6)))=0
                        THEN
                                NULL
                        ELSE
                                LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr6))
                        END as Agency_Email6 ,
                        CASE
                        WHEN
                                LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr7)) IS NULL
                                OR LEN(LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr7)))=0
                        THEN
                                NULL
                        ELSE
                                LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr7))
                        END as Agency_Email7 ,
                        CASE
                        WHEN
                                LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr8)) IS NULL
                                OR LEN(LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr8)))=0
                        THEN
                                NULL
                        ELSE
                                LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr8))
                        END as Agency_Email8 ,
                        CASE
                        WHEN
                                LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr9)) IS NULL
                                OR LEN(LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr9)))=0
                        THEN
                                NULL
                        ELSE
                                LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr9))
                        END as Agency_Email9 ,
                        CASE
                        WHEN
                                LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr10)) IS NULL
                                OR LEN(LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr10)))=0
                        THEN
                                NULL
                        ELSE
                                LTRIM(RTRIM(ae.email_addr10))
                        END as Agency_Email10                               ,
                        ta.last_modified                                    ,
                        ta.location_type                                    ,
                        ltrim(rtrim(ta.agency_fieldman)) as Agency_fieldman ,
                        case
                        when
                                agl.Id is null
                        then
                                'Cancelled'
                        else
                                'Active'
                        end as Status ,
                        row_number() over
                                          (
                                                  partition by LTRIM(RTRIM(ta.agency_num ))
                                                  order by ta.last_modified desc
                                          )
                        as rn         ,
                        ta.M_Address1 ,
                        ta.M_Address2 ,
                        ta.M_City     ,
                        ta.M_State    ,
                        ta.M_Zip
                from
                        dbo.Agency_stg ta 
                left join
                        dbo.AgencyLicense agl 
                on
                        agl.Agency_Id=ta.agency_nup
                left join
                        dbo.Member_Stg tm 
                on
                        ta.agency_nup = tm.members_agency_id
                LEFT join
                        dbo.Groups_stg tg 
                on
                        tm.members_group_id = tg.groups_nup
                LEFT join
                        dbo.GroupGuidewire_Stg gw 
                on
                        tg.groups_nup = gw.groups_nup
                left join
                        (
                                select
                                        d.name as DOM_name,
                                        d.id   as dom_value
                                from
                                        dbo.fieldreps_stg d)dd
                on
                        ta.agency_fieldman = dd.dom_value
                left join
                        dbo.AgencyEmail_Stg ae 
                on
                        ae.agency_nup=ta.agency_nup
                where
                        location_type='P' )a
where
        a.rn=1
order by
        Agency_nup asc--

parameters.name: $Lkp_Appointed_Dt$
parameters.label: DBConnection_SRC_Portal
parameters.customQuery:
SELECT t.agency_num as Agency_Num, appointed_date as Appointed_Dt,a.agency_alpha_workflow as agency_alpha_workflow
FROM agencyguidewire a
INNER JOIN t_agency t ON a.agency_nup = t.agency_nup
where a.status ='A'

parameters.name: $Lkp_Master_Agency_Detail$
parameters.label: DBConnection_TGT
parameters.customQuery:
select  Agency_ID as  Agency_ID
,ltrim(rtrim(Agency_Code)) as Agency_Code
,Agency_HashKey as Agency_HashKey 
FROM dbo.Master_Agency_Detail
where Row_End_Dt='9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'--

parameters.name: $Lkp_salesterritory_ref$
parameters.label: DBConnection_TGT
parameters.customQuery:
SELECT PMS_Sales_Territory_Group_Desc as PMS_Sales_Territory_Group_Desc
, salesterritoryrefid as salesterritoryrefid
, GW_Sales_Territory_Desc as GW_Sales_Territory_Desc
, GW_Sales_Territory_Group_Desc as GW_Sales_Territory_Group_Desc
, case when ltrim(rtrim(PMS_Sales_Territory_Desc))='Robert Knightly' then 'Bob Knightly' else ltrim(rtrim(PMS_Sales_Territory_Desc )) end as PMS_Sales_Territory_Desc
FROM dbo.SalesTerritory_Ref ----
